SUMMARY:US Open Fan Week
LOCATION:USTA Billie Jean King National Tennis Center\, Flushing Meadows\, NY
DESCRIPTION:Fan Week (Aug 23–29). Opens with Arthur Ashe Kids' Day. Qualifying Tournament and Mixed Doubles Championship run throughout the week. Free or low-cost grounds admission.
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
